###  http://datashapes.org/dash#SPARQLConstructTemplate
<http://datashapes.org/dash#SPARQLConstructTemplate> rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                                     rdfs:subClassOf <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#Parameterizable> ,
                                                                     <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#SPARQLConstructExecutable> ;
                                                     rdfs:comment "Encapsulates one or more SPARQL CONSTRUCT queries that can be parameterized. Parameters will become pre-bound variables in the queries." ;
                                                     rdfs:label "SPARQL CONSTRUCT template" .


###  http://datashapes.org/dash#SPARQLMultiFunction
